c: 27
v: 3
t: "why ayat trshd 'iilaa tariq alfawz fi aldunya walakhrt, wtbshr bihusn althawab lilmuminin aladhin saddaqu bha, wahtdawa bhdyha, aladhin yuqimun alsalawat alkhms kamilat alarkan, mstwfyt alshrwt, wywdwn alzakat almafrudat lmsthqyha, wahum yuqinun bialhayat alakhrt, wama fiha min thawab weqab"